Package: watershedtools
Title: Hydrologic Analysis Utilities Built on NHDPlus
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Chris", "Lyons", , "chris.lyons@ky.gov",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides HUC code validation and hierarchy resolution, watershed boundary retrieval, upstream and downstream stream tracing via 'NHDPlus' flow direction, pour point snapping, and feature-watershed spatial overlay. Built on 'nhdplusTools' for data access and 'sf' for spatial operations.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/chrislyonsKY/watershedtools
BugReports: https://github.com/chrislyonsKY/watershedtools/issues
